pageProps.description:
This is a really clean reliable  car and I'm selling it on behalf of my daughter who is in Australia originally staying for one year and now received sponsorship and is staying for two extra years . 
Please No time wasting , no  offers without viewing the car . 
The car is garaged in Ratoath Call Michael  on 0872547969 to view

pricePerMonth.displayText:
This calculation is provided as a guideline only. The information on the quotation is indicative and does not constitute a loan offer. APR stands for Annual Percentage Rate. Rate offered depends on loan amount and may differ from advertised rate. Lending criteria, terms and conditions apply. Over 18s only and not suitable for students.

The repayments on a personal loan of 8500 over 5 years with 60 monthly instalments are 173 per month at 8.3% variable (Annual Percentage Rate of Charge (APRC) 8.3%). The total cost of credit is 1880. Variable rates are correct as at 30th June 2020 and are subject to change. Bank of Ireland is regulated by the Central Bank of Ireland.
